net.beaconcontroller.web

Interface IWebManageable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoreWebManageable, DeviceManagerWebManageable, TopologyWebManageable

    public interface IWebManageable
    Interface to be implemented by bundles wishing to appear in the web UI.
    Author:
    Kyle Forster (kyle.forster@bigswitch.com), David Erickson (daviderickson@cs.stanford.edu)

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      String getName()
      The name assigned to this web manageable (usually the same method as the getName from IOFMessageListener).
      List<Tab> getTabs()
      Return tabs that will be rendered by the UI
